Products.RichDescription:
Goulburn Valley Australian Peaches Sliced in Mango Nectar contains no added colours, flavours or preservatives.

It takes a pretty special place to grow our mouth-watering Australian fruit.

A little bit of heaven on earth. Where the country's best available trees are planted into beautifully rich soil, given ample room to grow, showered with water and lovingly ripened under the radiant sunshine, until they flourish into delicious fruit. With a passion that's passed down from generation to generation. Our juicy ripe fruits as handpicked at the perfect moment, packed and proudly sent out. From the Goulburn Valley orchards to you.

Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Masterfoods Simmer Sauce Butter Chicken' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
MasterFoods Butter Chicken Curry Cooking Sauce is the perfect way to have a simple Indian curry any night of the week.

Preparation: 10 mins, | Cook: 5 mins, | Serves: 4

What You'll Need:
500 g Lean Chicken Thighs, cut into pieces
1 MasterFoods Butter Chicken Cooking Sauce
500 g Cooked Rice
Steamed Vegetables 

How to Cook:
1. Cut 500g of lean chicken thigh into pieces and cook in a non-stick pan until brown.

2. Add MasterFoods Cooking Sauce to pan and stir through. Simmer for 5 mins.

3. Serve with 500g cooked rice, steamed vegetables and a little yogurt. 

Refrigerate after opening. Use within 3 days.

This product has no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

Products.RichDescription:
Discover MasterFoods quick and easy Curried Sausages Cooking Sauce.

Create a simple, delicious dinner the whole family will enjoy. Created using a blend of delicious ripe tomatoes, onion and plenty of aromatic herbs and spices. Enjoy as part of your weekly diet.

Preparation: 5 Mins, | Cook: 10 Mins, | Serves: 4

What You'll Need: 
700g Sausages
1 Curried Sausages Cooking Sauce
400g of Mashed potatoes and Steamed Vegetables

How To Cook:
1. Cook 700g sausages in a non-stick pan until lightly browned. Remove and cut into pieces.
2. Return sausages to pan and add MasterFoods Cooking Sauce. Simmer for 5 mins.
3. Serve with 400g of mashed potatoes and steamed vegetables.

Refrigerate after opening. Use within 3 days.

Contains no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

Products.RichDescription: New flavour of Mama Bowl Instant Rice Noodles Soup series which presents an authentic Thai delicacy that many people around the world are passionate about. The broth truly unifies a host of favorite Thai tastes - sour, salty, spicy, and sweet. Aside from being one of Thailand's most famous soups, Tom Tum Goong has many health benefits due to its potent combination of herbs and spices.
